                    },
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/b/bb932a7c46778178d1cd9433fbc524c16441dd2b.png\" class=\"height-151-pixels width-128-pixels float-right\"/>Hier vind je de kennisbanken die horen bij deze opdracht.</p>\n"
